CADI.Client.Cache

Class ClientCacheManagement

  • java.lang.Object
    • CADI.Common.Cache.DataBinsCacheManagement
      • CADI.Common.Cache.CacheManagement
        • CADI.Client.Cache.ClientCacheManagement

  • public class ClientCacheManagement
extends CacheManagement
    This class implements the client-side cache management. It is based on the CacheManagement class providing an interface to access to the generic CacheManagement with methods more suitable for a JPIP client.

    Version:
    1.1.3 2011/09/05
    Author:
    Group on Interactive Coding of Images (GICI)
